    "body": "```solidity\r\n// contracts/Foo.sol\r\nimport \"./Bar.sol\";\r\n\r\ncontract Foo {}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\n// contracts/Bar.sol\r\nimport \"./Foo.sol\";\r\n\r\ncontract Bar {}\r\n```\r\n\r\n`hh compile` works, `hh flatten` doesn't.\r\n\r\nThe solution is probably to get some topological order of the dependency graph and to use that to generate the flattened file, ignoring previously visited files when resolving `import`s.",
